{"tid":2109304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華府擬廢除中美審計協議","createTime":"2020-07-15T06:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T08:22:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1141ca922b558edd42497ab5bca98158d5c4afa0","tid":2109304,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:56:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200715/TAMVWC3JAM3254HYUPZTJPRJRI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200715%2FTAMVWC3JAM3254HYUPZTJPRJRI%2F&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu5ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=c9b876c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200715%2FTAMVWC3JAM3254HYUPZTJPRJRI%2F&h=d177b2a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200715/TAMVWC3JAM3254HYUPZTJPRJRI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華府擬廢除中美審計協議<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VFkSkHYFbs7EfmCOPv0_nRKaNOA=/1280x796/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NMS2VA3W2DAAKG7TKUFWTX6HD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVFkSkHYFbs7EfmCOPv0_nRKaNOA%3D%2F1280x796%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNMS2VA3W2DAAKG7TKUFWTX6HD4.jpg&h=b2125f7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普政府被指支持廢除2013年中美簽署的交換審計文件協議。<br />\n<br />\n【本報綜合報道】路透周二引述消息人士報道，華府擬廢除中美之間的審計協議，料美方藉以打擊赴美上市及企圖規避美國會計審查的中概股。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中概股財務乏透明度<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。特朗普政府計劃支持廢除2013年中美簽署的交換審計文件協議。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院主管經濟事務、副國務卿克拉奇透過電郵回覆路透社查詢時指，華府即將採取行動，因為中資企業赴美上市，其財務資料和審計項目等均缺乏透明度。克拉奇又指，這是國家安全問題，不能再置美國股東於危險，將美國。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n於美國掛牌的中概股的財務造假及審計問題屢見不鮮，例如瑞幸咖啡陷入造假數醜聞。今年4月SEC發聲明指，PCAOB目前無法獲取中國境內的審計底稿，勸投資者注意投資中概股的潛在風險。"},{"pid":"c7c01dbaafb9d55ee8fcc3c44ce024021c049f06","tid":2109304,"uid":293225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:57:37.000Z","msg":"應該要啦，太多支那公司淨係識響美國上市吸錢但又唔交報表。<br />\n<br />\n應該趕呢班撚樣返支那。"},{"pid":"c96ad5a45ad322a69e95c6600c889cde60c0e09d","tid":2109304,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:58:46.000Z","msg":"黑狗馬賣國之作"},{"pid":"f6b353d1dbf7ba2412aa2f064e6d2d8ad4a1c235","tid":2109304,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:04:34.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f20939a5bc4d9ad3e840dcddaacb6d2f4a3435","tid":2109304,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:22:35.000Z","msg":"呢樣必須啦<br />\n賺幾多錢都話國家機密無得睇<br />\n一陣黎多次LK 2.0"}]}